title: Getting Go The Go Doc Project 2013.avi
description:
Getting Go - The Go Doc Project

A shy recent college grad devises to shoot a documentary about the NYC nightlife scene in order to meet the go-go guy he's cyber-obsessed with. the go doc project is a post-indie fusion of doc, narrative & art film forms. It's a fleeting summer fling in the city. It's fifteen minutes of fame. The video is great quality but just fyi it...
